data.description: Welcome to this amazing home! This gem is so deceiving; not a drive-by! You'll be so enamored immediately upon entrance you'll never want to leave. Beautifully & thoughtfully remodeled from stem-to-stern w/the utmost craftsmanship.  From the amazing detail of the ceilings to the gorgeous hardwood floors, quality wood crank windows, propane fireplace, perfect tiled in shower, built in aquarium, lovely landscaping....no stone left unturned. Room sizes are plentiful & surprising; open concept yet clearly defined; high ceilings & well-placed skylight allow natural light to stream throughout this home.  Attached carport coupled w/30 x 40 shop provides plenty of covered parking, tinkering & workspace. Deck out back for ultimate relaxation!
